  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Tormo Fregar</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Fregar\" title=\"House Fregar\">House Fregar</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tormo Fregar</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a> noble of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fregar\" title=\"House Fregar\">House Fregar</a>.   \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tormo_Fregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tormo_Fregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>, in the guise of the blind girl \"Blind Beth\", goes to the <a href=\"/index.php/Inn_of_the_Green_Eel\" title=\"Inn of the Green Eel\">Inn of the Green Eel</a>, the patrons state the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sealord\">Sealord</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ferrego_Antaryon\" title=\"Ferrego Antaryon\">Ferrego Antaryon</a>, is ill and when he dies Tormo Fregar will be the new Sealord. Later, when she tells the <a href=\"/index.php/Kindly_Man\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kindly Man\">Kindly Man</a> as a fact that Tormo Fregar will be the new Sealord, he reminds her that she merely overheard men drinking at the Inn of the Green Eel say that Tormo Fregar will be the new Sealord.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tormo_Fregar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, The Blind Girl.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403222216\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.059 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.231 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 431/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10382/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4419/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 208/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 530/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  222.980      1 -total\n 97.06%  216.427      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.16%  214.409      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.21%   24.985     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.56%    7.935      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.29%    5.103      1 Template:Ref\n  1.55%    3.466      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.57%    1.278      1 Template:References\n  0.45%    0.998      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:11444-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403222216 and revision id 285948\n -->\n",
